              <description><![CDATA[<p>Hello,</p>
<p>Luca Pacioli an Italian in 1494, published the first accounting book. Fast forward today every business in the world uses some method of accounting. Our accounting system has evolved and how we do accounting has also. Online and cloud accounting are the preferred method of accounting today.</p>
<p>With so many kind of businesses, professionals, freelancers what type of cloud accounting software will suit them best varies. We look at some of the Accounting Software providers and how they are using videos to market themselves and reach to their target audiences.</p>
<h2 class="h-custom-headline center-text h3 accent">XERO HQ LAUNCH VIDEO</h2>
<p>XERO equips you with the tools you need to better manage your clients, and unlock the insights you need to provide more advisory level services. Giving you the tools to streamline your practice, prioritise client work and gain insights into your client data. The launch video was used to highlight the whole new level of personalized accounting solution you can offer with the new XERO HQ platform.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
